# Business Logic

## Order States
Orders are tracked by the following states:
- Placed
- In Progress
- Ready To Serve
- Completed

## POS Screen
- User can tap on a button to add a menu item to an order.
- Some menu items will show an extra screen to configure the menu item, similar to Uber Eats.
- An editable, auto-incrementing order number will be added to each order.
- Optional: Add a name to the order.

## Orders Screen
- Group ordering of states is: Ready To Serve, Placed, In Progress, Completed.
- Orders can be fully edited on this screen.

## Kitchen Screen


- Show and manage the state for orders that are: Placed, In Progress, or Ready To Serve.